================
Poisson Approval
================


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/poisson_approval.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/poisson_approval

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/francois-durand/poisson_approval.svg
